overview.en: Wallet.cm is a blockchain wealth management wallet, including Bitcoin, Ethereum,EOS, etc., providing one-stop blockchain virtual asset management and wealth management. WCM wallet also supports quantitative trading and wealth management, cloud mining and wealth management, DAPP Game mining, and we also support one-click purchase of overseas funds, easy to achieve personal virtual asset allocation.
overview.zh: Wallet.cm是一款区块链理财钱包,理财包括比特币,以太币,EOS等,提供一站式的区块链虚拟资产管理理财,WCM钱包还支持量化交易理财,云挖矿理财,DAPP游戏挖矿,而且我们还支持一键购买海外基金,轻松实现个人虚拟资产配置
